    <defName>ShearlForager</defName>
    <title>Forager</title>
    <titleShort>Forager</titleShort>
    <baseDescription>[PAWN_nameDef] scrapes by with foraging. Combing the bogs and woods for plants of use and ambushing the occasional stray traveler.</baseDescription>
